title: 4 week animator contract
body:
Doodle ID for kudos: 7148

Discourse: https://forum.doodles.app/t/temporary-contract-for-doodles-animator/19

Rationale: Secure animation resources near-term to aid in social engagement and (confidential) partner discussions while we figure out hiring structure and creative support required for Doodle world-building.

Timeline: November 5th 2021 - December 3rd 2021

Goals: kick off creative world building with 3 reusable animated deliverables explained in above discourse thread. aiming for 200k+ twitter views total on all the content

Cost: 3.420 ETH to 0xDd5798dC0B309E8aC99Ce02d27e290f505B949C5

Accountability: Gnosis 2 of 3 multisig with Poopie, Tulip, Burnt as signers. Tulip and Burnt will be responsible for the hiring and project management.
